          <span class="badge">{igPostRows.length}</span>
          <span class="badge-sub">outcomes since each post date</span>
          <span class="info" data-tip="What each Instagram post produced on-site AFTER it went up. From IG = visits via the bio link (utm_source=ig) or a story link badge (utm_source=ig-story). Contacts = WhatsApp/call/email on that listing. This is the data that tunes the daily post suggestion.">?</span>
        </div>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table class="data-table">
